CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 29, 1958, pg. 6, reads: "11 Taverns in Five Blocks - Six of the 11 liquor dispensing establishments between Brushton and Lang Aves., on Frankstown Ave., a five-block area, are... (top right picture, left to right): The Metro Bar and the Rose Bar in the 7300 block... - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Freeman's Hat Bar and Rose Bar and Lounge, 7300 block of Frankstown Avenue at intersection of Sterrett Street, Homewood
